<h2 style="text-align: center; color: #C80000"><a name="ae"></a>ABOUT THE EDITOR</h2>
<p>Jonathan Bernstein is president & CEO of Bernstein Crisis Management, Inc., a national public relations agency specializing in crisis response, issues management and litigation consulting. It is also the only national PR agency able to create crisis- and issues-specific websites for its clients in as little as five minutes by employing proprietary PIER System technology. Information on the firm's services can be found by <a href="http://www.bernsteincrisismanagement.com/services.html" target="_blank">Clicking Here</a> or by calling (626) 825-3838. Information on its PIER capabilities can be found at <a href="http://www.crisiswebsite.com" target="_blank">www.crisiswebsite.com</a>.
