<h2 style="text-align: center; color: #C80000"><a name="jat"></a>JUST A THOUGHT</h2>
<p>"When it comes to managing crises, attorneys should be on the bus, not driving the bus."
<p><blockquote><i>Richard Levick, Esq., President, Levick Strategic Communications</i></blockquote>
